titles.title: An original resolution providing for members on the part of the Senate of the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.

calendar.text: Committee on Rules ordered to be reported an original measure.

action.text: Committee on Rules. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Ford. Without written report.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 1/28/1993--Introduced. Elects named Senators as members of the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.
